import React from "react";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import "./DailyWeatherInfo.css";
import clear from "./images/clear.svg";

export default function DailyWeatherInfo(props) {
    return ( < div className = "weatherColumn" >
        <
        Row className = "row border"
        id = "styleRows" >
        <
        Col className = "col-6 col-md-4"
        id = "daySpace" >
        <
        p className = "nextDay" > { props.day } < /p>  <
        /Col>

        <
        Col className = "col-6 col-sm-3"
        id = "weatherSpace" >
        <
        img src = { clear }
        className = "clear"
        alt = "weather-icon" / >
        <
        p className = "minMaxTemp" >
        Max: { props.maxTemp }°
        F <
        br / >
        Min: { props.minTemp }°
        F <
        /p>  <
        /Col>

        <
        Col className = "col-6 col-md-5"
        id = "tempSpace" >
        <
        p className = "dailyDescribeWeather" >
        <
        i > { props.weatherDescription } < /i>  <
        /p> <
        p className = "dailyHumidityText" > { " " } <
        i className = "fas fa-tint"
        id = "dailyHumidityIcon" >
        <
        /i> Humidity: {props.dailyHumidity}%{" "} </p >
        <
        p className = "dailyWindText" > { " " } <
        i className = "fas fa-wind"
        id = "dailyWindIcon" > < /i> Wind:{" "} { props.dailyWind }{ " " } 
        km / h { " " } <
        /p>  <
        /Col>  <
        /Row>  <
        /div>
    );
}
